# Naming
- Numeric prefix: `010_`, `020_`, `030_`, incremented by 10s.
- Use short descriptive names: `020_monthly_sales.sql`.
- Revisions: add `__v2` or date suffix.

# File header (template)
-- Title: <short description>
-- Intent: <what the query answers>
-- Inputs: <tables/views used>
-- Output: <fields and meaning>
-- Assumptions: <assumptions or limitations>
-- Validation: <how to verify correctness>
